headline: Serve Robotics Expands in South Florida, Launching Autonomous Deliveries in Fort Lauderdale with Uber Eats
summary: FORT LAUDERDALE, Fla., Dec. 05, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Serve Robotics Inc. (Nasdaq: SERV), a leading autonomous sidewalk delivery company, today announced the expansion of its service into Fort Lauderdale, marking a significant extension of its growing footprint in South Florida.
